==Russian==

===Etymology===
From Spanish [[albahaca]] < Arabic {{ARchar|[[حبق|الحبق]]}} (al-ħábaq), [[basil]], [[speedwell]].

===Noun===
'''альбаа́ка''' (albaáka) {{f}}, '''альба́аки''' (albaáki) {{p}}
# [[basil]], [[sweet basil]] (''Ocimum basilicum'')

